text: Hayley Preen (born 28 May 1998) is a South African road racing cyclist, equestrian and trail runner. She competed at the 2021 UCI Road World Championships, in the women's time trial event and women's road race event. She won multiple medals at the African Cycling Championships. She became South African National Road Race Champion in 2021. == References == Category:1998 births Category:Cyclists Category:Living people
